summary: Taylor keeps finding ways to make me feel prouder and prouder of her everyday. Everything she said in her post is everything I...
body:
Taylor keeps finding ways to make me feel prouder and prouder of her everyday. Everything she said in her post is everything I have, and will continue to believe in.

I believe Taylor rarely spoke about her political opinions for fear it would sway her fans to follow her lead, instead of making their own conscious beliefs and opinions, but I’m so proud of her for speaking out so open and honest.

I’m not American, but the issues Taylor spoke about are not solely American issues, they are worldwide issues, so if each of us can fight to make a change and a difference in the places where we live, we can each help to pave a way for the change that the world needs to see.

@taylorswift you have brought tears to my eyes and joy to my heart. I love you endlessly 💕
